S (TV series)|NCIS]]'', an American [[Police procedural|police procedural drama]] television series, premiered on [[CBS]] on September 24, 2019. The season is produced by Belisarius Productions and [[CBS Television Studios]].\n\n''NCIS'' revolves around a fictional team of [[special agent]]s from the [[Naval Criminal Investigative Service]], which conducts criminal investigations involving the [[U.S. Navy]] and [[United States Marine Corps|Marine Corps]].\n\nOn March 13, 2020, CBS announced that the filming of season 17 had been suspended due to the [[2019-20 coronavirus pandemic|Coronavirus pandemic]].<ref name=\"CBSCoronavirusSuspension\">{{cite web|url= https://popculture.com/tv-shows/2020/03/13/ncis-franchise-production-postponed-amid-coronavirus-outbreak/|title='NCIS' Franchise Production Reportedly Postponed Amid Coronavirus Outbreak|last=Levine|first=Daniel|date=March 13, 2020|accessdate=March 15, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> The season finale aired on April 14, 2020.\n\n==Cast and characters==\n===Main===\n* [[Mark Harmon]] as [[Leroy Jethro Gibbs]], NCIS Supervisory Special Agent (SSA) of Major Case Response Team (MCRT) assigned to Washington's Navy Yard\n* [[Sean Murray (actor)|Sean Murray]] as [[Timothy McGee]], NCIS Senior Field Agent, second in command\n* [[Wilmer Valderrama]] as [[Nicholas Torres|Nicholas \"Nick\" Torres]], NCIS Field Agent and former Undercover Agent\n* [[Emily Wickersham]] as [[Ellie Bishop|Eleanor \"Ellie\" Bishop]], NCIS Field Agent\n* [[Maria Bello]] as [[List of NCIS characters#Jacqueline Sloane|Dr. Jacqueline \"Jack\" Sloane]], NCIS Senior Resident Agent and operational psychologist\n* [[Brian Dietzen]] as [[Jimmy Palmer|Dr. Jimmy Palmer]] Chief Medical Examiner for NCIS\n* [[Diona Reasonover]] as [[List of NCIS characters#Kasie Hines|Kasie Hines]], Forensic Scientist for NCIS\n* [[Rocky Carroll]] as [[List of NCIS characters#Leon Vance|Leon Vance]], NCIS Director\n* [[David McCallum]] as [[Dr. Donald \"Ducky\" Mallard|Dr. Donald Mallard]], NCIS Historian and former Chief Medical Examiner\n\n===Recurring===\n* [[Cote de Pablo]] as [[Ziva David]], former NCIS Special Agent\n* [[Laura San Giacomo]] as [[List of NCIS characters#Grace Confalone|Dr. Grace Confalone]]\n* [[Megan Gallagher]] as Jennifer Leo, Under Secretary of the Navy\n* [[Don Lake]] as Phillip Brooks, Navy Captain\n* [[Louise Barnes]] as Mira Sahar Azam / Sarah, Gibbs' Neighbour and terrorist\n* Jack Fisher as Phineas, Sarah's son\n* [[Usman Ally]] as Victor Mir, NCIS target\n* Damon Dayoub as [[List of NCIS characters#Adam Eshell|Adam Eshel]], Mossad Officer\n* Elayn J. Taylor as Odette Malone, former CIA Operative\n* Kate Hamilton as Faith Tolliver, Jack Sloane's biological daughter\n\n===Guest===\n* [[Devale Ellis]] as Dante Brown, Kasie's childhood best-friend\n* [[Patrick Duffy]] as Jack Briggs, Retired Navy Lieutenant Commander\n* [[Kevin Kilner]] as Patrick Norian, NSA Access Manager\n* [[Lisa LoCicero]] as Elena Devol, Torres's girlfriend\n* [[Camryn Grimes]] as Laney Alimonte, Marine Corporal\n* [[Ellen Geer]] as Esther Daniels\n* [[Karri Turner]] as Micki Kaydar, Phineas' aunt\n* [[Daphne Zuniga]] as Stacy Gordon, Navy Commander\n* [[Christopher Lloyd]] as Joseph \"Joe\" Smith\n\n==Episodes==\n<onlyinclude>\n{{#invoke:Episode table|main\n|background  = #36454F\n|overall     = 5\n|season      = 5\n|title       = 24\n|director    = 15\n|writer      = 32\n|airdate     = 12\n|viewers     = 8\n|country     = U.S.\n|episodes    =\n{{#invoke:Episode list|sublist|NCIS (season 17)\n |EpisodeNumber   = 379\n |EpisodeNumber2  = 1\n |Title           = Out of the Darkness\n |DirectedBy      = [[Terrence O'Hara]]\t\n |WrittenBy       = Gina Lucita Monreal \n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2019|9|24}}\n |Viewers         = 12.57<ref name=\"17.01\">{{cite web|url=https://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/daily-ratings/tuesday-final-ratings-sept-24-2019/|title=''Black-ish'' and ''The Voice'' adjust up, ''New Amsterdam'' adjusts down: Tuesday 